@SpinTrack.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7001

### Register User - API v1.0
POST {{SpinTrack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!",
  "confirmPassword": "StrongPass123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "middleName": "Michael",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "nationalId": "123456789",
  "gender": "Male",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-15",
  "nationality": "USA",
  "jobTitle": "Software Engineer"
}

### Login - API v1.0
POST {{SpinTrack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
