### Query Users with Pagination and Filtering - API v1.0
POST {{SpinTrack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/users/query
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here

{
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "searchTerm": "john",
  "filters": [
    {
      "columnName": "Status",
      "operator": "Equals",
      "value": "Active"
    },
    {
      "columnName": "Gender",
      "operator": "Equals",
      "value": "Male"
    }
  ],
  "sortColumns": [
    {
      "columnName": "FirstName",
      "direction": "Ascending"
    },
    {
      "columnName": "CreatedAt",
      "direction": "Descending"
    }
  ]
}

